OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FThose numbers are not uncommon; a
OL,7,Fsurvey carried out by Public Health
OL,8,FJersey in 2024 found that more than a
OL,9,Fthird of students spend more than five
OL,10,Fhours a day on screens.
OL,12,FAn Ofcom study in the UK uncovered a
OL,13,Fsimilar trend, with children aged
OL,14,Feight to 17 spending between two and
OL,15,Ffive hours a day looking at screens on
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,18,FNearly half of that time is dedicated
OL,19,Fto watching content on platforms like
OL,20,FYouTube and TikTok.
