OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FThe average age at which children
OL,7,Ffirst see pornography is just 13 years
OL,8,Fold.
OL,10,FAlthough parents can manage settings
OL,11,Fon some devices to help protect their
OL,12,Fchildren's well-being, there are
OL,13,Fgrowing calls for governments to
OL,14,Fintroduce laws to restrict the amount
OL,15,Fof harmful content that is often
OL,16,Freadily available for children and
OL,17,Fyoung people to access online.
