OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FThe UK's Online Safety Act will come
OL,7,Finto force in July, but Jersey
OL,8,Fcurrently has no similar legislation
OL,9,Fafter opting to build its own laws
OL,10,Findependently.
OL,12,FThe UK Act involves a series of rules
OL,13,Faiming to protect children from
OL,14,Fcontent relating to topics including
OL,15,Fsuicide, self-harm, eating disorders
OL,16,Fand pornography.
OL,18,FBeaulieu teacher Mr Harris hopes the
OL,19,FITV News experiment can help highlight
OL,20,Fhow difficult it is to control what
OL,21,Fchildren can access online.
