OL,3,C'Addicted': The teenagers who gave up
OL,4,Ctheir phones for a fortnight
OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "I've got an 11-year-
OL,7,Fold at home, who will be starting
OL,8,Fsecondary school in September, and
OL,9,Fhe's just got his phone.
OL,11,F"We're very strict at home, so we
OL,12,Fmonitor his apps, but I'm sure there
OL,13,Fare lots of parents with the best will
OL,14,Fin the world who will not be able to
OL,15,Fmonitor and police that."
